/a306ffbb9dd1b6c7ebd82624fa8a0f40.webm?t=1745443880\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866630/extras/a306ffbb9dd1b6c7ebd82624fa8a0f40.mp4?t=1745443880\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866630/extras/365a8f15447e927db3b1d0d91923a1af.webp?t=1745443880\" width=400 height=20 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The strategic depth of drafting-roguelikes combines with streamlined experience of an autobattler. Each run offers new choices, new threats, and new opportunities to perfect the art of undeath. The path to power is paved with bones… will they be yours or your enemies’?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866630/extras/49e1b60577afed7027977d94089b1811.webp?t=1745443880\" width=400 height=20 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 60+ Unique minions with undying dedication </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 70+ Necromantic spells to sway combat in your favor </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 50+ Rewards to empower you as your reclaim your kingdom </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Numerous Castle Activities to add variety to your runs!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
